# Cloudflare Pages redirects
# https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/configuration/redirects/
#
# Evaluation order: first match wins. Static rules first, wildcards later.

# Maintenance mode (main branch only): all content pages bounce to root so
# visitors land on the "site launching soon" page regardless of entry URL.
# Static assets under /img/, /css/, /js/ are NOT matched (filesystem serves
# them directly). When the site is approved, restore the prior clean-URL
# rules (/about.html -> /about etc., see git history) and revert index.html
# from staging.
/index.html              /    302
/about                   /    302
/about.html              /    302
/course                  /    302
/course.html             /    302
/contact                 /    302
/contact.html            /    302
/apply                   /    302
/apply.html              /    302
/styleguide              /    302
/styleguide.html         /    302
/brand-rationale         /    302
/brand-rationale.html    /    302

# www apex canonicalisation is handled at the Cloudflare zone level
# (DNS + Redirect Rule), not here. Documented in
# docs/infra/cloudflare-setup-runbook.md Part 3.
